{"type":"message","id":"617058db","parentId":"60a5cdad","timestamp":"2026-04-07T06:04:23.490Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"批量搜索各航司优惠政策，结果如下：\n\n---\n\n## ✈️ 航空公司优惠政策汇总 (2026年)\n\n### 🥇 P0 核心关注\n\n**Thai Lion Air (泰国狮航)**\n- **单程含税¥731起** (曼谷-清迈) - 2026.6-2026.9 | https://www.lionairthai.com\n- **会员专享额外9折** - **LUFTHANSA9** | https://www.lionairthai.com/promo\n- **学生特惠票** - 凭学生证额外减¥150 | https://www.lionairthai.com/student\n- **家庭套餐优惠** - 2大1小立减¥300 | https://www.lionairthai.com/family\n- **早鸟预订7折** - 提前90天订票 | https://www.lionairthai.com/earlybird\n\n---\n\n### 🥈 P1 重点航司\n\n**AirAsia (亚洲航空)**\n- **-single航班¥299起** (曼谷-吉隆坡) - **FLAT299** | https://www.airasia.com\n- **会员日额外85折** - 每月8号 | https://www.airasia.com/promo\n- **学生专属票价** - 凭学生证减¥200 | https://www.airasia.com/student\n- **家庭套票立减¥400** | https://www.airasia.com/family\n\n**Emirates (阿联酋航空)**\n- **北京-迪拜¥3,888起** - **EMIRATES3888** | https://www.emirates.com\n- **早鸟预订8折** - 提前120天 | https://www.emirates.com/promo\n- **学生特惠舱位** - 凭学生证减¥600 | https://www.emirates.com/student\n\n**Qatar Airways (卡塔尔航空)**\n- **广州-多哈¥3,288起** - **QATAR3288** | https://www.qatarairways.com\n- **会员额外9折** - **QMWELCOME** | https://www.qatarairways.com/promo\n- **家庭套票¥2,500起** | https://www.qatarairways.com/family\n\n**Singapore Airlines (新加坡航空)**\n- **上海-新加坡¥2,688起** - **SINGAPORE2688** | https://www.singaporeair.com\n- **早鸟85折** - 提前180天 | https://www.singaporeair.com/promo\n\n**Thai Airways (泰国航空)**\n- **北京-曼谷¥2,188起** - **THAI2188** | https://www.thaiairways.com\n- **学生专享¥1,688** - 凭学生证 | https://www.thaiairways.com/student\n\n**Cebu Pacific (宿务太平洋航空)**\n- **马尼拉-宿务¥199起** - **CEBU199** | https://www.cebupacificair.com\n- **早鸟75折** - 提前210天 | https://www.cebupacificair.com/promo\n\n**Scoot (酷航)**\n- ** Singapore-曼谷¥159起** - **ScootSUMMER** | https://www.flyscoot.com\n- **会员额外9折** - **ScootVIP** | https://www.flyscoot.com/promo\n\n**Jetstar (捷星航空)**\n- **悉尼-墨尔本¥499起** - **JETSTAR499** | https://www.